column3: “As a person with 100% disability from combat-related PTSD, I can tell you that this is the first strain that I have found that has actually decreased my reliance on PTSD meds the doctors give me. Since I started using Skywalker, I no longer need to pop a Xanax when I am feeling stressed-out (which is usually daily!). I take a couple good tokes of this and I'm good-to-go again! This stuff rocks!!!”

“I smoked this for about a week with a coiled vaporizer pen.  It was pretty good.  However, once I got a true vaporizer and tried it, it was a different story.  Let me start by saying I suffer from different types of mental and physical ailments.  I smoked skywalker with a true vape and it was like a full body massage for over 4 hours.   I felt completely better for DAYS afterward; my anxiety has left, depression has ...”

“Peace, people. I am massively picky with my strains because I can slip into paranoia quickly due to incredible anxiety.  My bipolar mind can shut my creativity down without notice. To the rescue came this beautiful strain! Beginning in the head it took a trip down to my body and brought with it pure relaxation and calming effects. Focus, desire to write and being content with life all joined the party. My sleep was f...”

“Sweet, hairy little nugs... People seem to be emphasizing the strange sorta space you enter on this one. Rightfully so. 
My supply of this strain was nit of the highest quality -- pretty to look at but extremely subtle aroma. Very dense and smokes well. 
The high caught me off guard, hit me straight in the frontal.lobe like it wanted to pull my head into the ground. I felt verrrry relaxed. The head high slowly crept ...”

“Grown on Tatooine by Owen Lars, he named it after his wife. Popular amongst Jedi smokers, this one really helps you connect with what surrounds us, penetrates us and binds us all together. On Tatooine this strain is referred to as Power Converters" and can be picked up at the dispensary inside Toshi station. The Hookah Lounge in Mos Eisley sells it as a house brand. Very popular in Degobah.”"

“Bought 2g of this at 27.7% thc from my local dispensary. smell and flavor are mild but nice and smoke is incredibly smooth on the throat. As far as the effects, it definitely pays tribute to its blueberry and afghani parents. very heavy and sedating and spacey. if you are an indica lover or patient seeking pain relief or need a good sleep aid, this will do you no wrong. i've found a new favorite with skywalker and wi...”

“A superior strain.  Mentally stimulating.  Your body feels incredible.... that light, floaty feeling magnified.  Verged on the psychedelic after three small bowls from the Arizer Solo.  Should be a fan favorite for all who know and love sweet sweet cannabis.  Definitely buying again.”

“One of the most impressive highs from a hybrid. 
Its light and airy, yet at the same time has great taste and does not leave any trace of fatigue or grogginess like some strong Indicas. 

Definitely NOT for amateur smokers.

9 out of 10; hands down a top favorite.”

“Illinois THC rate 19%. The only time I had the pleasure of this indica was right after I had my wisdom teeth pulled. I was in an extreme amount of pain and wanted to be knocked out. Of course that day my store was out of gorilla glue.  So I asked for the next best thing and oh boy I got it. 
I figured with a name like skywalker you would feel up- lifted . No , it a very heavy , downer , knock out the pain and put you...”

“Name: Skywalker Og



From: **Censored until I recieve permission from clinic to advertise their location and/or name of business.**



Grade: A



Type: Indica



Price: $$213/half ounce



Looks: Golf sized buds with lots of crystals.



Smell: .6 is enough to dank up my room with the smell. Very unique smell compared to other strains I can recall, I can't quite put it into words.. by my god, it smells strong.


Ta...”
“It's a nice mellow high made me relax and not stress. Good indica because it doesn't make you too lazy”

“this is really getting me high like I could use the force like Luke Skywalker- that was his review.
Mine? It's alright. Good head, nice body relaxing.”

“Picked up about 3.2 grams of this just a few days ago from a new connect. This strand looks fluffy and the texture is slightly crystallized. After about 3 good hits you're out. Out of mind, out of sight. You feel like eating, one small joke can trigger the longest laugh to the point where it would make our cheeks hurt and falling asleep while on Skywalker feels like you're walking the sky. First of two strands that m...”
“I got a gram of Skywalker kush shatter and the high was nice very good but the come down tends to leave me with a headache. (I tried smoking and vaping it)”

“yessir!! this strain is everything other reviews are saying: it's simply amazing! a most excellent indica crossbreed of blueberry & mazar and yet it surprisingly does NOT keep you glued to the couch and wanting to pass out or pig out..it's an all around kickass high that's heavy in the body but not to heavy in the head..makes you feel very uplifted and all around terrific :-D”

“This is my go to.

I am Bipolar II with depression and Anxiety. This Knocks me out and takes down my crazy manic highs.

Flower, Oil, wax. Its My personal favorite. I'll drive 20 + miles to get it.”

“A quick high, with defined stages:
1. Head rush
2. Relaxation 
3. Creative/Engaged
4. Hungry
5. Tired

Not an energetic strain, but doesn't put you to sleep.”

“This was my first time trying out Skywalker, it looked amazing and smelled very potent. I am an everyday toker, so I wasnt expecting anything special to come from this. 2 bong hits later and I cant remember what I was doing.  It's on my list now, I loved it.”

“Truly great strain for relaxing and meditation. It doesn't give you that fuzzy head high or why am I in the kitchen now feeling. Just really nice mellow high that truly relaxes the body. 

I had hurt my lower back and had to stop my yoga for a while and this stuff was the best medicine to take away the constant ache and let me focus on other things. Really the most relaxing strain I've had and try to keep on hand.”
“Skywalker is basically Ambien. Out like a light after smoking. Caused some paranoia after using nightly for a week...kept thinking something was watching me in the dark.”

“One of the most potent strains we have had the privilege of carrying.  The effects are fast, this is not a creeper. The high was all upper body at first, everything appears clear and your senses feel heightened. Before you realize it, your entire body is feeling the affects and you are simply along for the ride from this point. Enjoy it, it's a good ride. I don't recommend this strain for beginners. Skywalker OG shou...”

“It comes on nice and smooth athen a rush simmilar to a coffee, rush but kind of makes you into a baked feeling where almost everything is feeling nice like I can move all the joints in my body, I can stand on a strain like this for hours and not feel a thing great for sitting or standing if you have a desk job all the time or are glued to the computer like me. Leaves me dizzy bit encouraged :p.”

“This strain is OK. It's smooth and it gives you a nice body high. In my opinion it's not that strong. Relaxing for sure. High doesn't last long. Great for Anxiety. Might buy again. It's more of a daytime smoke. You can still do things not couch locked.”
“Gives a very good mellow high. Puts you in your own world and not thinking about anything else. Makes you very hungry. Great for a daily night time blunt before bed!”

“It comes on nice and smooth athen a rush simmilar to a coffee, rush but kind of makes you into a baked feeling where almost everything is feeling nice like I can move all the joints in my body, I can stand on a strain like this for hours and not feel a thing great for sitting or standing if you have a desk job all the time or are glued to the computer like me. Leaves me dizzy bit encouraged :p.”
“Gives a very good mellow high. Puts you in your own world and not thinking about anything else. Makes you very hungry. Great for a daily night time blunt before bed!”
“I found the Skywalker strain gives a good, relaxing high. It has a major side effect of causing dry mouth, however. All-in-all a very chill experience full of feeling light and carefree.”

“Smoked from pipe.  Seemed slower to hit me.  Calm relaxed feeling.  Then i felt like i was rocking myself but i swear i wasnt moving. Lol  i then started to feel warmness in diff parts of body.  Dry mouth.  Show on tv had me laughing hysterically.  Anxiety/panic attack gone!  Slight anger gone.  All negative thoughts are blocked.  Just laying here enjoying the lightness of my body (im morbidly obese seriously lol)......”

“Skywalker is truely an amazing strain, with its huge fruity nugs, taste is incredible, it's a very euphoric Indica that really does calm ya down after a long day concerning the Force! This is a definite favorite on my end.”
“Made me feel like my face was melting...in a good way.”
“I love this strain. One of my favorites! It helps you relax yet you have such mind to do things. Focused and very chill mind high. Good for music, playing games, movies etc”
“High comes on very fast, I barely slept the morning I smoked this and felt like shit, after smoking I had a general feeling of wellness, with no bad feelings.”

“Picked this up from Glendale Greenhouse, AZ. I love this smoke when it's time to go to sleep. Kind of hard to say how long the buzz lasts, because I'm usually out cold within 30 minutes of smoking. Great relaxer that mellows you out, turns off your brain and lets you sleep through the night! This and Grand Daddy Purple are probably my two favorite sleepy time strains. Enjoy!”
“one of the best sit on your ass weed strand love it!”

“I've been told on many occasions that Skywalker is indeed a sativa dominate bud, however the strain I received felt nothing like a sativa, so YMMV.  The flowers were generously covered with milky crystals, and beautiful vibrant orange hairs.  The smell was a strong pine with a hint of citrus, almost like lemon pinesol.  Not the most pleasant, but pretty unique.  Taste was smoother than the smell, with a lemon sour sw...”
“this indica has got me funked up. she tap dances in my head then pause only to repeat... while my body surrenders to power of this relaxing dizzing bud.”
“There's a big difference between Skywalker (I) and Skywalker OG (H). Skywalker (I) is a heavy hitting Indica that results in a near perfect state of relaxation and relief for bed time.”

“May the force breath in you!
        The size of Skywalker's buds aren't anything  to brag about but they pack a lot of punch being so dense and light. The aroma is very earthy with a touch of berry once you crack 'em open.
        The green hit is sweet and almost smoky, not to harsh and complimented with good clean expansion. The second hit stacked amazingly, tasted like the blueberries roasted into cranberries.
  ...”
“Skywalker is definitely a great high. I'm not super experienced, but so far Skywalker is definitely my favorite strain.”
“It's a really nice flower, has a sweet, pungent smell to it, the smoke to me is really smooth not harsh at all, heavy hitter that's  for sure!!”

“Skywalker is more like an OG strain to me, because of its stanky OG smell.  It gives a very nice head-numbing high, with a great taste and an effective body high.

A lighter hitting OG, Skywalker cannabis is uniquely found to be fluffy, with short brown hairs and predominantly frosty petals surrounded with random dark petals, giving it that world-class flavor.”
“It's a really nice flower, has a sweet, pungent smell to it, the smoke to me is really smooth not harsh at all, heavy hitter that's  for sure!!”
“Great indica. Probably one of the best for pain and sleep. Great for when you are getting ready to go to bed. Puts you on couch lock hard.”
“Skywalker is definitely a great high. I'm not super experienced, but so far Skywalker is definitely my favorite strain.”
“The force is strong with this one.”

“The first thing that stands out about skywalker is it's sweet, butterscotch like aroma. The high starts off with a sativa like head high but stays mellow and doesn't cause anexiety like a full sativa. After 30 minutes or so the effect turns more indica and begins to relieve pain and relax the user followed by increased appetite and finally the need to sleep. Skywalker is the perfect strain to unwind after a long day,...”

“My absolute favorite strain! Great for insomnia, anxiety, depression and stress. Heavy high, very relaxing and laugh-inducing. Don't recommend it for daily activities, but perfect for late nights or before big meals. Smells amazingly dank too.”
“Stop reading reviews and go buy some Bubba Skywalker.You will thank me later.”

Very body relaxing as well as slowly the stress leaves you and relaxation hits. It’s perfect all day every day.”

best med in my personal opinions”

“I had the original Skywalker, the offspring of Mazar and Blueberry. Definitely one of my top favorites. The taste and smell are unique - quite hashy and harsh (even after perc'ed through water) but it had a very powerful orange flavor to it as well. Very zesty. The high is a heavy Indica body stone. The front of your head feels tingly, and you really just want to lie down and listen to music. The high is also very ha...”

“One of my personal favorite strains another purple Indica similar to Granddaddy Purp but balanced out a little bit more being a hybrid. The buds are beautiful and look almost alien with their purpley hue. This strain could stop your pain say if your Sith Lord father happened to chop off your arm with a light saber...”
“Definitely a very chill strain. Good for end of day and a good movie night.”
“The Force is strong with This one! I've enjoyed this strain a couple of times, and have not been disappointed. Must try.”
“This was a great strain. Made me very uplifted and happy. Again, no let down as is typical w/ OG crossed strains. Will get again.”

column1: My ideal night starts with me
column2: vaping on some Skywalker to feel relaxed. Boy
column3: does it make me feel gooood. I then make sweet love to my wife
column4: because

column3: “I have had this twice, from two different co-ops and I really like it. Depending on the batch, the high was very good and strong. I noticed that my sense of hearing was increased but in a good way. Wind chimes especially sounded neat. Flavor is smooth almost soapy but its not a bad flavor.”
“Forgettable flavor.  Vague hints of grapefruit/tropical fruit.  That being said, pretty darn good for relaxation.”
“I was able to down an entire pizza after smoking a pre-roll of this strain. The scent is so wonderful- like a blueberry cobbler with savory notes. Completely relaxing as well.”
“Lovely nightcap Cannabis here!”

“skywalker had me feelin like jedi hitting hyperspeed in the millennium falcon in the best way possible but the indica evens it out and keeps u mellow wouldnt recommend trying to destroy the death star after consuming some of this might hurt your focus”

“***SKYWALKER O.G. REVIEW***   I've always been curious about this one given the fact that I have NEVER been IMPRESSED by ANY Star Wars themed/named strain like Master Yoda for example. When my dispensary told me that they were going to be getting a fresh batch of this strain in I figured I'd give it a run. Very nice. Not too heavy at all for an OG strain. A nice reative sativa high rolls along with a steady body high...”
“One of my favorite strains. It melts away the stress and just leaves you feeling very connected to those around you. Comfortable in your own skin really.”
“Forgettable flavor.  Vague hints of grapefruit/tropical fruit.  That being said, pretty darn good for relaxation.”

All anxiety and pain was GONE, I felt super uplifted as well. Took a little long to kick in, but once it did it was absoloutely incredible. Truly felt as if I was a Skywalker in the sky, 5/5”

“i have to post another rating because this strain is out of this world. ive stopped taking my bipolar and sleeping tranquiliser for 2 weeks now because skywalker has solved all my ailments. it is great before work and it pumps you up and puts you ahead of the game. ive also managed to stop a long drug use of OTC syrup which gave me energy to just get through another day.  ive been on it for 14 years now and if i didn...”
“This strain looked and smelled good, but the taste was bad and the smoke was kinda harsh.”

“Skywalker! That name will always be known around the world. Unfortunately this strain will be not quite known for the time being. This particular strain is very good for someone starting their journey into the Budlands". It's very gentle on the throat and lungs. The flavor is a bit on the sage-piney side
column4: but very tasteful nonetheless. It would leave me feeling pretty uplifted and happy with a bit dry mouth. i stron...”"

column3: “When fresh, great full body high”
“It has a light almost citrus taste, felt a happy light" feeling buzz. It helped with some light aches and pains.”"

“I get my skywalker from Strawberry Fields in the Springs. I just smoked some and I. AM. SO. STONED. The budtenders know what they're talking about. It's great for pain, nausea, headaches, anxiety and all around recreational use. God, I love this strain. Every time they get a new batch I get as much as I can. It's so good.”
“friggin great run. tasty and decent stone.”
“All of my patients come back ranting and raving about this strain. It's on the stronger side and it gets them where they need to be.”
“Definitely a different high then I have ever experienced. The name suites it well. You feel like your a skywalker". Great indica
column4: no couch lock more like a lifted daze but knocks you out. Great after a long day of work when your body aches and you just wanna sleep peacefully.”"

column3:
“This is a great strain for body pain!!! 
Head stays clear and your body will just feel light and airy. 
Enjoy!”

“On the second hit most of my pain has begun to subside.  Still thinking clearly at this point.  This will give me a very relaxed feeling and a better sleep.  This doesn't last as long as I would like though for pain control.”
“Strong in the force this one is”
“Deserving of its given name. Leads to the true path of enlightenment. There is definitely a strong force with this one.”
“One of the smoothest buds I've ever smoked. Feels great with a strong, comfortable high. One of my favorites.”
“this is the shit i got  the concentrate version aand added it to green goddess strain and it makes my head weightless, very euphoric and great for bedtime bowls.”

“I acquired this from Green Thumb. Everyone was very pleasant, patient, and helpful. People who leave bad reviews about how people don't know what they are talking about" fail to realize that just like a doctor these people don't know what a particular stain is going to do for YOU. Everyone is different and reacts to medicines differently. My experience was ecstatic with these people!”"
“Very nice hybrid. Upon first smoking it I noticed it was a little hard to hit, but a very nice dense bud with lots of THC.”
“MY FAVORITE”
“Great, quick hitting high. Knocked us both into a great nights sleep with no morning weed haze. First time use - I might have a new favorite Indica!”
“Just left Herbal Remedies as usual im very satisfied.”
“This is good pot”

“finally found my favourite strain. puts you on a very chilled buzz that helps with body pain, stress, happiness and gives you good energy. ive been on the hunt for this strain as it really helps a lot and lasts for a long time (+- 4hrs) . try it today, you won't be sorry.”
“Very good tasting strain”
“been moonwalking since yesterday!”
“Only took a few hits to feel the unworldly effects of Skywalker.  This pungent strain brings me a rush of euphoria only moments after smoking.  Couch lock is brutal.”
“Best bud i've had in a while.”

“Much like the Sativa Strain.  Only difference is the OG makes the body feel good and the Skywalker makes you ready to blow up the Death Star!”
“From Local Products was great”
“A high that gives you a good amount of energy and makes gives you a floaty feeling.  Its a indica dominant hybrid that has the best of both sativa and indica.”

“I didn't see Skywalker OG strain, so I'll post my comments here. This strain is bomb! It's taking off in Nor Cal and is sure to be a new trendy strain before long. Too bad clones are impossible to find… Although it's nothing special to look at, the high is intense. It's mostly cerebral and puts me in my Happy" place. This is my favorite day-time strain right now.”"
“One of my fav. Strains .”
“All I can say is that I LOVE this stuff!!!”
“amazinggggg. Would recommend to first time indica users.”
“Had a dab of this and was gone on a magical journey!”
“best weed i have ever had one joint and 3 bong rips i was done”
“lol so high I forgot about the rating”
“Great indica shawty”
“Awesome strain, super relaxing and great for smoking really anytime.”
“Lately, this has been one of our regulars. Nice buzz, good on pain relief and relaxing. Helps me sleep.”
“Great strain. I suffer from insomnia and this puts me to sleep every time. Very relaxing and stress relieving.”

“Good strain for the indica heavy lover, the batch I got isn't tops so 4 stars is the best I can give this BATCH. I would give this STRAIN 5 stars and a strong A im sure if it were top shelf. A lot of my strains rate high because I know what I like and have had most before.  Heavy hitter, had me coughing a little and I dont usually cough. Very pungent aroma, relaxing medicine. No feelings of anxiety and I have thyroid...”

“Medium-sized buds, pretty dense, orange hairs and orangey crystals.  I detect a very sweet, honey-tangerine scent straight away.  Earthy/pine undertones, slightly sour citrus scent.  The flavour is not as pronounced as the scent in my opinion but a nice taste.  I was pleasantly surprised by how Skywalker relaxed my muscles after just one bowl.  The high was mellow, nothing mind-blowing.  Overall I'm happy with it but...”
“Got 0.8g for $10. Veeeeery lazy strain, gets you super relaxed but not very good for anything else. Looks like a great option for people who use it to relax and for pain relief.”
“One of my favorite night time Vape or flowers”

“What I smoked: Liquid Dreamers Indica Cartridge

My experience: the high was very similar to its description. It came on pretty quickly with just one hit. It was nice after a long day at work to come home and have a few hits off my vape pen. It's definitely a head high, but doesn't leave you all hazy afterwards like most indicas. I will definitely keep this on my list of favorites.”
“Very earthy pungent smell. Over whelming head high. Also feel very energized. Very good strain to smoke any time.”
“Very sweet taste and super relaxing.”
“I just tried Skywalker in honey vape form and it's smooth yet strong. awesome for end of day chill session.”

“Great hybrid, good body high with the indica, but a good slight sativa high as well, not too harsh or strong. has beautiful buds as well.
overall I would give it 4.8 out of 5 stars”
“Oh lord this is by far the strain the works best with my body. Very intense body melt feeling and euphoria this is one strain to keep on hand”
“pretty heavy indica, it's not for productive days. this strain is def for when you want to get stoney baloney and giggle a lot.”
“I smoked this with my friends in his hottub, and wow, couldnt stop cracking up! Love it <3”
“Not bad - but won't be one of my favorites.”

“Skywalker is truely an amazing strain, with its huge fruity nugs, taste is incredible, it's a very euphoric Indica that really does calm ya down after a long day concerning the Force! This is a definite favorite on my end.”
“Nice blend of body and heady high. Tingly sensation all over. Not the best for pain, but a very nice high.”
“I highly recommend this strain!!  It's phenomenally uplifting yet relaxing.  Good cure for the worries.”
“A great strain helps me get thru the pain and puts me to sleep.”

“i know every collective in los angeles has skywalker on the menu some even 15 a g but this gcut" Skywalker TLC got puts the rest to shame ! light green pungent sticky crystal covered buds make for great shmoke and at $10 a g definatly a come up”"
“so far the best for my migraines ♡”

“When smoked in large amounts, which for me is killing an eighth in one night with my friends, the effects are far more sedative and kind of trippy. When not smoked as much, the effects are still really relaxing, but not paralyzing haha. Over I like this strain a lot, but not as much for trying to get really fucked up, although you don't need a lot to get stoned haha.”
“This very potent strain has an awesome taste and awesome effects. A definite favorite.”
“Helpful”

“If you need to throw down on homework or practice....well anything this bud will keep you active, focused and there's not a crash, I went for a jog yesterday while smoking on this yesterday and felt great after. I was anticipating a crash or body high and was a tad bummed that there wasn't a body high.”

“IMHO, this is a top notch strain, fairly potent, good in small to medium doses. I felt very relaxed but still focused. It is an excellent augmenter to relaxing activities, including meditation. I also got the munchies, and the eats were gooooood. Great strain all around.”

“Easily one of my favorite strains and it hits like a truck. Easily got two veterans very stoned and feeling good. Great for pain and just all around relaxing. Not a preferable day time smoke less you use very little and maybe mix it with a higher sativa.  All and all though it really uses 'the force'. 

I plan to get a few clones around for sure I love it so much.”
“love it amazing blueberry smell and taste is great too”
“Hard to believe it is a Indica. Very sweet, Smell is stong. Great for just relaxing.”
“One of the best body relaxers I have ever experienced.”

“Effect: TKO.  Okay to vape, but tread lightly.
Color/density: Light gray forest green, lots of orange hair. dry, not very sticky, breaks up easily.
Taste/smell: Earthy taste, slightly lemony. Smells like Ramune candy”
“beautiful, nice body high, relaxing and mental focus”
“Smooth berry pine and mint. Calm relaxed and clear headed with a mild euphoria. Good for reflection and creativity. Relaxed but not lethargic. Relaxes my neck and back nicely”

“Great smoke, could last a little longer though.”

“Genetics: Mazar X Blueberry 

Type: Hybrid (Indica dominant) 

Looks: Small dark tight buds with huge pods covered in trichomes. 

Smell: At first its almost like smelling a diesel strain but it has a slightly sweeter aroma. 

Taste: It’s actually opposite than the smell, which I thought was kind of weird. It starts out tasting a little sweet like a berries but then has a sour aftertaste.”

feel tired teh following dayy”

I've also tried sfv og, sweet tooth...”

I like to keep some hash around for a little ex...”
“fire”
